{"tid":1159271,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人病左會自己買抗生素食？","createTime":"2019-05-17T14:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T14:45:10.000Z","uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a7cccce3410c5eae7e519b138a1f1025dfbde10b","tid":1159271,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講病左唔好亂食抗生素<br />\n但睇開個醫生每次普通感冒發燒佢都會開抗生素比我<br />\n我而家諗緊病左好唔好自己去藥房買抗生素食算，反正比咁多錢佢都係開返果啲藥<br />\n同埋佢開果隻抗生素真係好勁，食完第2日已經冇晒事<br />\n<img src=\"https://medicarcp.net/website/images/Products/2918%20-%201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicarcp.net%2Fwebsite%2Fimages%2FProducts%2F2918%2520-%25201.jpg&h=1073e91d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b03d50c567b56a6203312d94c6ba3c966934aa0","tid":1159271,"uid":193893,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"好快有抗藥惡菌，巴打最好食足一個療程"},{"pid":"d3fe957356c94866da545b64b20c58fe094a4c78","tid":1159271,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"1b03d50c567b56a6203312d94c6ba3c966934aa0","tid":1159271,"uid":193893,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:25:15.000Z","msg":"好快有抗藥惡菌，巴打最好食足一個療程"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:27:42.000Z","msg":"我每次都會食足個療程，都怕自己會養到超級細菌<br />\n不過主要怕副作用，因為抗生素好似會連體內既益菌都殺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0249e933d9c3ce4b118cf87f4ef69677cda1d8e3","tid":1159271,"uid":111559,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"其實傷風感冒係病毒引起 抗生素係打細菌引起既病 唔好亂食 有病就睇返醫生 一個唔覺意亂咁食 令到有超級惡菌就唔好啦 中學sci都有教切勿濫用抗生素<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945f2996ea18d9e88235484f0af637ad673dba4f","tid":1159271,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3fe957356c94866da545b64b20c58fe094a4c78","tid":1159271,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"1b03d50c567b56a6203312d94c6ba3c966934aa0","tid":1159